data.description: BUYERS FINANCING FELL THOROUGH! Inspections complete! Welcome to the highly desired Cypress Bend. This high end custom home is equipped with stainless steel appliances including new dishwasher and granite counter tops throughout. 4 bedrooms 3 bathrooms, new wood like tile in the open concept living room and kitchen area. One of a kind outdoor fireplace is perfect for entertaining especially with the cooler nights ahead. New roof 2020. This home is located in a gated subdivision and in the highly desired Benton school district. QUALIFIES FOR RURAL DEVELOPMENT! Schedule your private tour today!
